			<abstract>
				<p>Testimony of 31-year-old Dr. A.K. on his hardships as a labor serviceman in the Hungarian Army on the Eastern front in 1942/43,
					where he deserted along with 41 comrades and joined the partisans.</p>
			</abstract>
		</profileDesc>
